      <title>Foucault’s Prediction of ‘Live and Let Die’</title>
      <category domain="https://www.newsdeeply.com/refugees/laws-policy/">Laws &amp; Policy</category>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Apr 2016 06:33:04 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>Stephane J. Baele</author>
